<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8213900>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Spatiodamaeus kalugaensis sp. nov., adult: A—dorsal view (exuvial scalps and legs not shown); B—ventral view (gnathosoma and legs not shown). Scale bar 200 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8213900/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8213902>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Spatiodamaeus kalugaensis sp. nov., adult: A—habitus, right lateral view (exuvial scalps not shown); B— right lateral view (exuvial scalps, gnathosoma and legs not shown); C—subcapitulum, ventral view; D—palp, right, antiaxial view; E—chelicera, left, paraxial view. Scale bars 200 μm (A, B), 50 μm (C–E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8213902/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8213906>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Spatiodamaeus kalugaensis sp. nov., adult, microscope images: A—dorsal view (exuvial scalps removed); B— ventral view; C—right lateral view (exuvial scalps removed); D—bothridium and some prodorsal setae, lateral view; E—scalps on notogaster; F—part of epimeral region, ventral view; G—part of epimeral and anogenital regions, ventral view. Magnification 200 (A–C, E), 1000 (D, F, G)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8213906/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8213904>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Spatiodamaeus kalugaensis sp. nov., adult:A—leg I, right, antiaxial view; B—leg II, right, antiaxial view; C—leg III, left, antiaxial view; D—leg IV, left, antiaxial view. Scale bar 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8213904/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8213918>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Spatiodamaeus kalugaensis sp. nov., juvenile instars, microscope images:A—larva, dorsal view; B—deutonymph, dorsal view; C—deutonymph, ventral view; D—deutonymph, right lateral view. Magnification 200." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8213918/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8213908>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Spatiodamaeus kalugaensis sp. nov., larva: A—dorsal view (some notogastral setae broken; legs not shown); B—ventral view (some notogastral setae broken; gnathosoma and legs not shown); C— right lateral view (gnathosoma and legs not shown); D—subcapitulum, ventral view; E—palp, left, paraxial view; F—chelicera, left, paraxial view. Scale bars 100 μm (A–C), 20 μm (D, F), 10 μm (E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8213908/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8213916>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Spatiodamaeus kalugaensis sp. nov., tritonymph: A—dorsal view (notogastral setae broken; exuvial scalps and legs not shown); B—ventral view (some notogastral setae broken; gnathosoma and legs not shown). Scale bar 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8213916/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8213914>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Spatiodamaeus kalugaensis sp. nov., nymphs: A—protonymph, ventral view (gnathosoma and legs not shown); B—deutonymph, ventral view (gnathosoma and legs not shown). Scale bars 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8213914/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8213912>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Spatiodamaeus kalugaensis sp. nov., larva: A—leg I, right, antiaxial view; B—leg II, right, ventroantiaxial view; C—leg III, left, ventroantiaxial view. Scale bar 20 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8213912/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

